name: ReInvenTrip Daily Adventures #001 - When the Color Goes Out
description: We all have those days when the color goes out. Tomorrow will be better! Day 1 of Reinventing prior versions of myself. Work I created over 20 years ago, being revisited and reinvented for the NFT space on HEN. Based on a copper etching done in South Dakota in the late 1990's. [Twitter: @AyZe]
